Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么重新打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好吗 Cygnus的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没变呢 费尔米博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 前方有舰艇接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联结系统实验舰Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:03.88,zm,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(656,488)}联结实验舰Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到Cygnus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常欢迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 美丽的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看您这么精神我太开心了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸上又添小皱纹啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 恕我唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结系统的公开表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们能展示给费尔米博士看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎是为了这个才特地从夏威夷赶来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从夏威夷来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们很快就要抵达的夏威夷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不愿再等下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 LUXON现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好座舱区域没有损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是可能联结的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老爷子就是联结系统的开发者呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确来说应该是开发小组的领队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出联结理论的确实是费尔米博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是以博士的研究室为主体 开发了系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之所以能够实用化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要归功于所员艾维拉小姐开发的座舱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我是好处都被徒弟拿走的糊涂师父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博…博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是糊涂师傅不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在艾维拉君的爷爷那里开始联结的基础研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 从她还裹着尿布的时候就认识她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她裹尿布一直裹到很大年纪 大家都很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 那个小姑娘现在却是远在我之上的研究者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能不高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有段佳话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲谈就到此为止吧 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,emphatier振动数安定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enharmonic控制竟然能完成到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结的持续时间是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实用界限值300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距解除联结还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除联结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统和驾驶员都没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 青叶君 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你骗得了机器 别以为就能骗过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么骗不骗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那座岛上见到了那个叫雏的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要编那种一戳就破的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 她不是我认识的雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 在70年后的这个世界里 没有雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我 把我送到未来的弓原雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才失落的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有失落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意外还挺纤细的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说我没失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 敌方驾驶员知道回过去的方法这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从哪里听说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是小学生都能编个更好的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是编故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想哭丧着脸到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUXON已经修理完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样的家伙还是不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭丧着脸的 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前不久还在为妹妹烦恼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少在那里自以为是的教训别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟菲奥娜没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 你这个不干脆的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打啦 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 你这家伙 放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让这家伙清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真能给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩有点做过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长说让你们暂时在这里冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我做多余的运动啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 费尔米博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你是从过去来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是70年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你不相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于联结系统你了解多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是将两个驾驶员的大脑并联
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞越提高演算能力的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个系统的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在于令两人的思考毫无延迟地传达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为时滞会影响战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思考毫无延迟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么对那个笨蛋说明都是白费力气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 因为现在仅仅隔着一面墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这样交流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在战场上可不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离越远延迟越大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是纳秒等级的延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为损害联结的诱因也足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们是怎样联结的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时空移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道思考的传达会产生1纳秒的延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将思考传送至1纳秒未来 问题就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事有可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本粒子等级的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本粒子等级？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 博士还是不相信你的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人看上去关系不错 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在新型机上面搭载联结系统？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听说吗 很快就要读出了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还只有两台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人物们古板的脑袋 也有点松缓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 联结机的量产也近在眼前了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 还没到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为联合没有重视联结系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是被敌人紧逼不放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为佐基利亚有那个人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样 老师研究室的一个研究员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃亡去了佐基利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个优秀的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定深知艾维拉君的座舱的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:14.26,zm,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,400)\pos(666,484)}佐基利亚科学院第2实验研究所所长 比卢海鲁姆·哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪卢海鲁姆·哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是一个非常有趣的作战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我去和行政所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 哈恩博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油 玛格丽塔特务武官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说 这可能是最后的机会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你奋战到底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Slave 佐基利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是本次作战的概要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐 哈恩博士到底是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一介科学家 竟然能在行政局跟前说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你们应该知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我将亲自上阵指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就拉你上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我想让你拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 一脸复杂的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你是怎么从那座小岛发出信号的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从接到信号 到我们抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没有花费很久的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 FORTUNA的座舱已经沉入大海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从联合的新型机那里发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我在森林里找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正想要夺取的时候敌人却回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只发出了求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我身上没有武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那座岛上 没有FORTUNA以外的valiancer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们到达之前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我藏起来了 所以没怎么看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说 难以置信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太碰巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事跟中佐说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要告诉中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被特务武官阁下先察觉就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要早点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都会相信你的只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方valiancer正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至接触为止还有10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体 对空战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来 要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 把那种状态的两个人放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 从一开始不就一直是那个样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不要想多余的事 集中精神战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我当然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶同学 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请开始联结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数高热源物体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佐基利亚的巡航导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nectar屏障展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损害如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部轻微受损 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cygnus的nectar屏障的填充来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机 尽可能打落导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间惊讶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着吧雏 这家伙由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Crane中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康拉德大尉 将飞向Crane的导弹全部打落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许继续中弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事 Crane不会因为这种程度就沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾维拉君 我已经把你爷爷教我的东西全部告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该到你毕业的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来就托付给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多怎么打得完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说丧气话 做该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是青叶同学和迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 只要等敌人打完导弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能打完就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是准备了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目标是联结时间终了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据哈恩博士的预测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个新型机的联结持续时间是300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 还有90秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是解除联结 这数量可不是闹着玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手别停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹还在继续飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 联结已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃 渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是决定留在Cygnus上战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个笨蛋 而且无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 自己决定的路无论发生什么都要继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在Cygnus需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 拥有回应这种需要的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吧 为了需要你的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 你这爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 穿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说我没有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自以为是教育别人了 你这个妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 明明失落到不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在模仿你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 哪壶不开提哪壶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人一边吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边打落了那么多的导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 时间已经不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距解除联结还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结被维持了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特务武官阁下 请指示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续发射导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有误差而已 联结不可能持续很久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射发射发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联结持续时间已经超过400秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹全部被迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱…脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开 打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是应该死在这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧 特务武官阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗里德·加兰特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机回舰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 爱哭鬼 你还挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦 妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的联结持续时间是429秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信 竟然远远超过了理想值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾维拉君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是优秀的联结哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 行政局似乎决定了你的调动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近期就会有联络的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前好好休息一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人羡慕啊 我有多少年没有拿到休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈恩博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 阿尔弗里德中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅既然进入了夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法再使用正攻法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想实施之前呈报的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呈报？什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经跟上面说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和那个部队立刻会合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待你哦 阿尔弗里德中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Slave 佐基利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时期派增援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊 里亚赞少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:41.82,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(650,479)}下回「父与子」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 父与子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,心的呼应 响应的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛的理由 请暂且忘记 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,我深知你 我在一直寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻吻向那已飘渺的光的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那稍稍的犹豫不决 成为了那连接希望的蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了与那温柔黎明的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,想去拯救 想去保护 那早已归还于天空的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步 那已经早已传达过梦想的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能与我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的爱
